	* blib/butils.h: cosmetics

2004-01-04 22:24  neo

	* configure.in, docs/reference/tmpl/bview-aa.sgml: Fixed configure
	  output for the case aalib is not available.  Updated docs.

2004-01-04 13:30  neo

	* blib/bmovieplayer.c: Reverted the last change. The library should
	  never print any error messages (yes I know there are a few places
	  that still do). It's up to the caller to do that.

