2003-02-06 16:58  neo

	* blib/bpacket.c, blib/bpacket.h, docs/reference/tmpl/bpacket.sgml:
	  Converted b_packet_hton() and b_packet_ntoh() to regular
	  functions.  Trying to write portable inline functions obviously
	  didn't work and I doubt it will make any noticeable difference
	  anyway.

