	* modules/bclock.c: Fixed stupid typo in BClock.

2002-12-31 19:32  neo

	* modules/bcountdown.c: Include <sys/time.h> for gettimeofday().

2002-12-31 19:29  neo

	* modules/bcountdown.c: Use gettimeofday() for more accurate
	  timing.

