	  docs/reference/tmpl/bprotocol.sgml: Removed
	  b_module_info_scan_default_dir(). Pass NULL to
	  b_module_info_dir() to get this behaviour.  Changed
	  b_sender_remove_recipient() so it only removes recipients with a
	  matching port number.  Changed b_sender_list_recipients() to
	  include the port number.  Added more docs (77%).

