	  modules/bqix.c, modules/btetris.c, test/test-module.c,
	  test/test-movie-player.c, test/modules/test.c: Changed the
	  modules once again. The packet member of the module object has
	  been replaced by a simple buffer which is width * height bytes.
	  A module always has channels == 1 and maxval == 255 (for now).

