	  0.7.	Fixed wrong handling of loop element in BML parser.

2002-09-06 02:58  neo

	* ChangeLog, NEWS, README: Made 0.6 Release.

2002-09-06 02:28  neo

	* gfx/bview-gtk.c: Ughh, gdk-pixbuf seems to have some bad bugs in
	  the composition code :-( The routines seem to be OK for bilinear
	  sampling, so use those. Use gdk_pixbuf_copy_area() whenever
	  possible.

