2002-08-27 01:45  neo

	* blib/bmovie-blm.c, blib/bmovie-bml.c, blib/bmovie-gif.c,
	  blib/bmovie.c, blib/bmovie.h, test/test-movie-parser.c: Changed
	  BMovie API: b_movie_new() takes one filename and generates a name
	  from it.  movie->name is the printable version and may be altered
	  using b_movie_set_name(). movie->filename is the filename used to
	  open the file (and should never be output).

